OL,3,CHead chef jailed for sexual offences
OL,4,Cinvolving girls aged 13 and 16
OL,6,FThe head chef at an Indian takeaway in
OL,7,FSt Ives has been jailed for sexual
OL,8,Foffences involving two teenage girls.
OL,10,FRajon Ahmed, 40 and from St Ives, was
OL,11,Fsentenced at Exeter Crown Court after
OL,12,Fpreviously being convicted at Truro
OL,13,FCrown Court.
OL,15,FDuring the trial, it was heard how
OL,16,FAhmed was well aware the victims in
OL,17,Fthe case were aged 13 and 16.
OL,19,FHis first victim was the younger girl.
OL,20,FHe followed her on social media,
OL,21,Foffering her cigarettes and cannabis.
