OL,6,FAhmed then sent her explicit images of
OL,7,Fhimself. Ahmed and the victim met
OL,8,Ftwice and on the second occasion, he
OL,9,Fkissed her and touched her
OL,10,Finappropriately.
OL,12,FAfter this, he communicated with the
OL,13,Folder victim on social media and
OL,14,Foffered her cigarettes.
OL,16,FOn one occasion he hugged her and
OL,17,Ftouched her inappropriately as she
OL,18,Fmoved away.
