OL,4,Cinvolving girls aged 13 and 16
OL,6,FAhmed was convicted by a jury of
OL,7,Fsexual assault, sexual communication
OL,8,Fwith a child, and two counts of sexual
OL,9,Factivity with a child.
OL,11,FHe was found not guilty of a second
OL,12,Fsexual assault charge.
OL,14,FAhmed was sentenced to 16 months in
OL,15,Fprison. He will also be subject to a
OL,16,FSexual Harm Prevention Order for seven
OL,17,Fyears, and be on the Sex Offenders
OL,18,FRegister for 10 years.
