OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing, Detective
OL,7,FInspector Andrew Shorten said: "I
OL,8,Fwelcome today's result and I am
OL,9,Fgrateful to the victims in this case
OL,10,Ffor supporting this investigation over
OL,11,Fa protracted period of time.
OL,13,F"I would also like to thank West
OL,14,FCornwall Public Protection Unit for
OL,15,Fthe comprehensive investigation which
OL,16,Fhas brought this offender to justice
OL,17,Fand prevented further harm.
