OL,6,F"I hope this case reassures the
OL,7,Fcommunity how seriously the police
OL,8,Ftake reports of Child Sexual Offences
OL,9,Fand gives people the courage to come
OL,10,Fforward in future."
OL,12,FPolice staff investigator Steve Panter
OL,13,Fsaid: "There is a real fear that the
OL,14,Fpattern of his offending would have
OL,15,Fescalated had it not been for the
OL,16,Fcourage of the victims and witnesses
OL,17,Fto come forward and challenge his
OL,18,Fbehaviour when they did.
